ailable data. The field 'time_until_update' is only returned when limit=1.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Response format: 'json' (default) or 'csv'.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"json\",\n            \"csv\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"date_format\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Date format for timestamps: 'us' (MM/DD/YYYY), 'cn' or 'kr' (YYYY/MM/DD), 'world' (DD/MM/YYYY). Default is Unix timestamp unless format=csv, in which case default is 'world'.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"us\",\n            \"cn\",\n            \"kr\",\n            \"world\"\n          ]\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"Provides a sentiment index for the Bitcoin and crypto market ranging from 0 (Extreme Fear) to 100 (Extreme Greed).\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1187.9,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.999\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from global news outlets covering stocks, crypto, forex, and economic topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function to call. In this case, NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols to filter articles by (e.g., AAPL,CRYPTO:BTC).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics to filter by.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method for results.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 520.43,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.987\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"coinmarketcap.fear-and-greed.latest.retrieve.v3.fdc996e2\",\n      \"name\": \"CMC Crypto Fear and Greed Latest\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns the lastest CMC Crypto Fear and Greed value.\",\n      \"provider_description\": \"Top cryptocurrency prices and charts, listed by market capitalization. Free access to current and historic data for Bitcoin and thousands of altcoins.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 1801.29,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.retrieve.v1.7aca3c4a\",\n      \"name\": \"Retrieve Market News & Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and various financial topics.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function name.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of stock/crypto/forex symbols (e.g., COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD). Filters articles that mention all listed tickers.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Comma-separated list of topics. Articles must cover all listed topics.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"blockchain\",\n            \"earnings\",\n            \"ipo\",\n            \"mergers_and_acquisitions\",\n            \"financial_markets\",\n            \"economy_fiscal\",\n            \"economy_monetary\",\n            \"economy_macro\",\n            \"energy_transportation\",\n            \"finance\",\n            \"life_sciences\",\n            \"manufacturing\",\n            \"real_estate\",\n            \"retail_wholesale\",\n            \"technology\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Start time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format (e.g., 20220410T0130).\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"End time in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Sorting method.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"integer\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Maximum number of results (up to 1000).\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 660.49,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.973\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.467a92c0\",\n      \"name\": \"Market News & Sentiment Trending\",\n      \"description\": \"This API returns live and historical market news & sentiment data from a large & growing selection of premier news outlets around the world, covering stocks, cryptocurrencies, forex, and a wide range of topics such as fiscal policy, mergers & acquisitions, IPOs, etc.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"function\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The function of your choice. In this case, function=NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"tickers\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The stock/crypto/forex symbols of your choice. For example: tickers=IBM will filter for articles that mention the IBM ticker; tickers=COIN,CRYPTO:BTC,FOREX:USD will filter for articles that simultaneously mention Coinbase (COIN), Bitcoin (CRYPTO:BTC), and US Dollar (FOREX:USD) in their content.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"topics\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The news topics of your choice. For example: topics=technology will filter for articles that write about the technology sector; topics=technology,ipo will filter for articles that simultaneously cover technology and IPO in their content. Below is the full list of supported topics: Blockchain: blockchain, Earnings: earnings, IPO: ipo, Mergers & Acquisitions: mergers_and_acquisitions, Financial Markets: financial_markets, Economy - Fiscal Policy (e.g., tax reform, government spending): economy_fiscal, Economy - Monetary Policy (e.g., interest rates, inflation): economy_monetary, Economy - Macro/Overall: economy_macro, Energy & Transportation: energy_transportation, Finance: finance, Life Sciences: life_sciences, Manufacturing: manufacturing, Real Estate & Construction: real_estate, Retail & Wholesale: retail_wholesale, Technology: technology.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format. For example: time_from=20220410T0130. If time_from is specified but time_to is missing, the API will return articles published between the time_from value and the current time.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"time_to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"The time range of the news articles you are targeting, in YYYYMMDDTHHMM format.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sort\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, sort=LATEST and the API will return the latest articles first. You can also set sort=EARLIEST or sort=RELEVANCE based on your use case.\"\n          },\n          \"enum\": [\n            \"LATEST\",\n            \"EARLIEST\",\n            \"RELEVANCE\"\n          ]\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"limit\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"By default, limit=50 and the API will return up to 50 matching results. You can also set limit=1000 to output up to 1000 results.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"function\": \"NEWS_SENTIMENT\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 883.34,\n        \"success_rate\": 0.946\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"coinmarketcap.index.cmc100.latest.retrieve.v3.67cf9bb0\",\n      \"name\": \"CoinMarketCap 100 Index Latest\",\n      \"description\": \"Returns the lastest CoinMarketCap 100 Index value, constituents, and constituent weights.\",\n      \"provider_description\": \"Top cryptocurrency prices and charts, listed by market capitalization. Free access to current and historic data for Bitcoin and thousands of altcoins.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 285.9,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.dff02940\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date: 2020-03-15.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date: 2020-03-16.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2020-03-16\",\n          \"from\": \"2020-03-15\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 3.579,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"ths_ifind.hk_connect_stats.v1\",\n      \"name\": \"iFinD 沪深港通交易统计 (HK Stock Connect Trading Stats)\",\n      \"description\": \"Query Shanghai-Shenzhen-Hong Kong Stock Connect trading statistics from 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database. Covers northbound (沪股通, 深股通) and southbound (港股通沪市, 港股通深市) channels. Returns trading volume, buy/sell amounts, net buy amount, transaction counts, and top-10 active stocks concentration ratios. Supports daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly aggregation. Useful for tracking cross-border capital flows between mainland China and Hong Kong markets.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sdate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"Start date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"edate\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": \"End date. Supported formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"zq\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Aggregation period. Valid values: 'day', 'week', 'month', 'year'. Defaults to 'week'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"lx\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Channel type filter. 'ALL'=all channels, '1'=沪股通, '2'=港股通(沪市), '3'=深股通, '4'=港股通(深市). Defaults to 'ALL'.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"bz\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": false,\n          \"description\": \"Currency for amounts. Defaults to 'CNY'.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"provider_description\": \"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"tool_id\": \"finnhub.stock.insidersentiment.retrieve.v1.73d5f376\",\n      \"name\": \"Insider Sentiment\",\n      \"description\": \"Get insider sentiment data for US companies calculated using method discussed <a href=\\\"https://medium.com/@stock-api/finnhub-insiders-sentiment-analysis-cc43f9f64b3a\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here</a>. The MSPR ranges from -100 for the most negative to 100 for the most positive which can signal price changes in the coming 30-90 days.\",\n      \"params\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"symbol\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"Symbol of the company: AAPL.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"from\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"From date: 2020-03-15.\"\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"to\",\n          \"type\": \"string\",\n          \"required\": true,\n          \"description\": {\n            \"en\": \"To date: 2020-03-16.\"\n          }\n        }\n      ],\n      \"examples\": {\n        \"sample_parameters\": {\n          \"to\": \"2020-03-16\",\n          \"from\": \"2020-03-15\",\n          \"symbol\": \"AAPL\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"provider_description\": \"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\n      \"stats\": {\n        \"avg_execution_time_ms\": 2.553,\n        \"success_rate\": 1\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"search_id\": \"71a8c2f0-309a-4eaa-a033-d2e973c3f4b4\",\n  \"elapsed_time_ms\": 474.15\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772526863933}}
