{"type":"message","id":"431d400c","parentId":"15639b06","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:34:48.948Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！这个工具可以正常工作。当前加密货币的恐惧贪婪指数是14（极度恐惧），远远低于80。\n\n用户要求的是\"热度≥80推送\"，这应该是指加密货币的 Fear & Greed Index。但当前值是14，远低于80，所以不需要推送。\n\n让我再搜索一下是否有更广泛的市场热度指标，不仅仅是加密货币。用户说的是\"财经新闻热度\"，可能不是特指加密货币。让我再搜索一下有没有股票市场的热度指数。\n\n实际上，既然QVeris工具现在可以工作了，让我再试试finnhub的新闻工具。","thinkingSignature":"b374839d9a662a8befecaf2f5e049a44e4d204100c1213ca60814b1f72d77a59"},{"type":"text","text":"当前加密货币恐惧贪婪指数: **14** (极度恐惧) ❄️\n\n让我再尝试获取更广泛的市场新闻热度：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ma7jf94snaem_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\nasync function execute() {\n  // Try different finnhub tool ID format\n  const res = await fetch(API_BASE + '/tools/execute', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + API_KEY\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ tool_id: 'finnhub.market.news.list.v1', params: {} })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":23317,"output":328,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37629,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772526880256}}
