{"type":"message","id":"ea4a71c3","parentId":"754d8440","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:34:57.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Fnnhub工具还是有问题。让我看看Alpha Vantage的情绪工具是否可以用不同的方式调用。Alpha Vantage返回的新闻情绪数据里有\"relevance score\"之类可以当作热度指标。\n\n让我再试一次Alpha Vantage，这次不带任何参数试试看：","thinkingSignature":"34b64eabbfb50852b6eac4f39092f994fae07b905da593f4fee7bb4ef85f351b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zymwc13q66ph_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(API_BASE + '/tools/execute', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + API_KEY\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'alphavantage.news_sentiment.query.v1.7aca3c4a', \n      params: { \n        function: 'NEWS_SENTIMENT',\n        topics: 'financial_markets',\n        limit: 25\n      } \n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":90}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":23779,"output":273,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38036,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772526890706}}
