{"type":"message","id":"40d9d3be","parentId":"07a8106d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:35:10.575Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Alpha Vantage工具也不行。看起来这些带function参数的工具有问题。但是alternative.me的恐惧贪婪指数可以工作。\n\n当前加密货币恐惧贪婪指数是14（极度恐惧），远低于用户要求的80阈值。\n\n由于：\n1. Finnhub新闻工具无法正常工作（参数传递问题）\n2. Alpha Vantage新闻情绪工具也无法正常工作\n3. 唯一能获取的\"热度\"数据是加密货币恐惧贪婪指数，当前值为14\n\n这种情况下，没有任何热度数据达到80，所以不需要推送。\n\n让我检查一下是否有其他工具可以获取市场热度。不过根据用户要求使用QVeris finnhub，如果finnhub不工作，我应该报告这个问题。\n\n让我总结一下情况：\n- 当前加密货币 Fear & Greed Index: 14 (Extreme Fear) ❌ 远低于80\n- Finnhub 新闻工具无法正常工作\n- 没有其他市场热度数据达到80\n\n结论：不需要推送，因为没有热度≥80的内容。","thinkingSignature":"58d4332064308da1fa05a8c06d6f857ce870d5fcf8f0c2d6718621a2bee02e9c"},{"type":"text","text":"由于 QVeris Finnhub 新闻工具参数传递存在问题，目前我能获取的可靠热度数据如下：\n\n**当前加密货币恐惧贪婪指数: 14 (极度恐惧)** ❌ 远低于80阈值\n\n让我再尝试一个替代方案获取市场情绪：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_34yxm0vvo91b_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace && node -e \"\nconst API_KEY = process.env.QVERIS_API_KEY;\nconst API_BASE = 'https://qveris.ai/api/v1';\nasync function execute() {\n  const res = await fetch(API_BASE + '/tools/execute', {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: {\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n      'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + API_KEY\n    },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ \n      tool_id: 'coinmarketcap.fear-and-greed.latest.retrieve.v3.fdc996e2', \n      params: {} \n    })\n  });\n  const data = await res.json();\n  console.log(JSON.stringify(data, null, 2));\n}\nexecute();\n\"","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":24181,"output":436,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38601,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772526899453}}
